‚úÖ Facebook group post generated at 12 PM?
Friday:

‚úÖ Email follow-ups check ran at 9 AM?
7.3 Error Handling
If a cron job fails:

Check OpenClaw logs: openclaw logs --agent <agent-name>
Run the agent manually to debug
Check environment variables are still set
Verify configuration files haven't been modified
Check Telegram for error notifications
Common issues:

Missing environment variables
Configuration file syntax errors
Network issues (ESP, WordPress API)
Rate limiting
Insufficient permissions
